message.body: How do you feel about accompanying Kalev and I during our commemoration performance?

We're trying to do a throwback medley and compile all the billboard hits seen 1995 into one big song...but it's kind of falling flat because we don't have anything to keep a beat so if you could work with us and construct a backup with your guitar that would be AMAZING AMAZING AMAZING
I could give it a shot! Might work better on keyboard but we'll see. Tomorrow I won't be in the practice rooms because I have an AP exam, but maybe Thursday or Friday we can practice.
Yeah keyboard is also great. Cool!!
Also how do you sign up to play at commemoration? The Flying Bins were thinking of performing
Talk to shank and he'll sign you up
